overview: Internet-RC.com is a one-stop shop for all RC vehicle enthusiasts. Our store has all kinds of radio controlled toys, from cars, boats and all kinds of aircraft. We sell racing cars, buggies, monster trucks, motorcycles, helicopters, jets, boats and blimps. We also have complete sets of RC vehicle gears and accessories such as motors, engines, chargers, batteries, transmitters, receivers and other essential parts. We carry the best brands in the market such as Mattel, Maisto, Fisher-Price, Jada Toys, Traxxas, Megatech, Cobra, Air hogs, and many more. Whatever you need to maintain or upgrade you RC, Internet-RC.com has everything you need. Store owner Robert, took good care of all his toys and more than 20 years later. His collection, which came from varied sources, continues to grow with his current addiction on RC vehicles. With his passion for toys, Robert decided to put up a store which offers radio controlled vehicles of all sorts, and that is how Internet-RC.com was born.
